overview: Besides offering a fascinating "Travels" section to Sydney, Australia, Logic #10 shines a light on new skateboard riders and pros alike. See profiles of riders such as up-and-comers Phil Mackie, Jason Jones, Van Wastel and Jim Gorecky, as well as heavy hitters Satva Leung and Gailea Momolu. A must for any skateboarder's collection.
title: Logic Skateboard Media: Vol. 10
